  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients safety and high Quality Performance built up the centre of anesthesiology. Standard&#xD;
      operating procedures based on the Helsinki declaration may help to increase the Patient&#xD;
      safety and decreased adverse Events or complications.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The Primary endpoint is the comparison of a Intervention Group with audiovisually blended&#xD;
      learning concept and a Standard Group receiving the Standard operating procedures via E-Mail&#xD;
      and Confirmation when reading.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
